      { question: 'Can I integrate EuroSalary data into my existing HR systems?', answer: 'Yes. Our REST API provides JSON-formatted salary data with endpoints for individual lookups, batch queries, and comparison matrices. We offer pre-built integrations for Workday, SAP SuccessFactors, and BambooHR, plus a generic webhook for custom platforms.' },
      { question: 'How fresh is the salary data?', answer: 'Our data pipeline combines four sources updated at different cadences: Eurostat (quarterly), job board postings (weekly), OECD indicators (bi-annually), and anonymous user submissions (real-time). We run a full recalculation on the first of every month.' },
